lenders.name: Gabriel
lenders.loan_because:
I have been working in a tourism industry for about 6 to 7 years. Most of i have been working as hotelier. For some time i wanted to change a career and therefore i went on to work as tour operator, where i can arrange tour to some destinations in Tanzania. We are blessed with different natural resources like big national parks, mountains, islands like Zanzibar e.t.c. Many of you have heard about Kilimanjaro mountain, Serengeti national park and even Zanzibar, these are attractions that are located in Tanzania. Therefore i have been coordinating and preparing some itineraries for different destinations. For the people who wished to climb The Kilimanjaro mountain or going on beautiful safari. So ever since the Ebola, threat as well as the Al Shaabab came across east Africa and Africa in total many bookings have been canceled and the tourism is quite low compare to some years back. We don't only want to blame that on this outbreak it can be some other reasons, economical issues for the travelers, bad services, big competitions from other big companies  and e.t.c

Therefore i have not been doing so good with almost no bookings made and then i decided to work as tax driver. In this way, i thought it will be much more easy to still work as tour operator as well as tax driver.

I am writing to you about all this because i would like that this loan i will get, will help me buy a small min van. 

In this case, the money i will get from the tax and transport business will help me do some quality marketing for the small holiday company that i run and get as much bookings as possible, which means this will not only help me live my dream but also helps to create jobs for my fellow youth around my town

Thank you all.
lenders.occupational_info: I am a 26 years old father and a husband. Working hard to help out my little family, i am so thankful for everything that have and do not have. I believe in working hard always the achievement rate is high on the goal that i make. So here i am....

lenders.occupational_info: Cześć. Mówią na mnie Mario, mam 20 lat, pochodzę z Kielc, jestem zapalonym fascynatem nowoczesnych technologi, w wolnych chwilach, programuję aplikację na windows phone. Wykonuję też pozycjonowanie Kielce oraz inne miasteczka na terenie całej Polski.

lenders.name: NxtGen Jr. High Group
lenders.loan_because: Our Group of 12 - 15 year old students have the desire and passion to help out people in countries all over the world.
lenders.occupational_info: NxtGen is a group of Immigrant Jr.High students in Calgary trying to make a difference in their schools, communities and world. Students raised money in their schools for various fundraisers in order help multiple people around the world. A lot of students have come from the same countries as the people they are lending money too. This is one of the ways they are trying to make a difference in the community, city and world around them.
